    <p>
        Trek In West Bengal Is A Unique And Unforgettable Experience.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Scenery</h4>
    <p>
        Besides, The Spectacular Sights Of Lofty Mountains Like Everest, Kanchendzonga, Chamlang, Makalu, Baruntse, Kokthang And Several Other Peaks Makes Your Trekking Expedition A Lifetime Experience. 
    </p>
    <p>
        Highest Mountains In The World Like Everest And If You Want To See These Up Close, You Must Walk. While Trekking You See Far More Than The Mountains. You Can Walk From The Alpine Meadows Brilliant Rhododendrons And You May See Rare Species Of Birds.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">People</h4>
    <p>
        Trekkers Are Always Impressed By The Friendliness Of The People They Meet Along The Local Trails .The Hill People Particularly Their Traditional Hospitality And Fascinating Culture, Make Trek A Special Kind Of Mountain Holiday Unlike Any Other Part Of World.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Safety</h4>
    <p>
        Not Only Is Scenery Interesting And Ever Changing But It Can Be Seen In Relative Safety. Theft, Robbery, Assault All The Problems Of Western Civilization And Many Asian Countries Are Unknown Here 
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Height</h4>
    <p>
        There Are Always Well-Developed Trails Through Villages And Across Mountain Passes.
        So The Trails, Though Often Indistinct, Are Always There. All Trails Are Easily Traversed Without The Aid Of Ropes Or Any Mountaineering Skill.
        Techniques Are Almost Never Used On A Traditional Trek. Anyone Who Has Walked Extensively In The Mountains Has All The Skill Necessary For Trek.
    </p>
